text:
Kamu pasti udah denger masalah Kominfo yang mengancam akan memblokir Google, Facebook, Whatsapp hingga Instagram kalau enggak mendaftar jadi PSE. 

Tapi, kenapa sih ini harus diramaikan? Emang apa sih masalahnya? Nah, berikut kami rangkumkan hal-hal yang perlu kamu ketahui. https://t.co/fUxfdLEril
en_text:
You must have heard the problem of the Communication and Information Technology that threatened to block Google, Facebook, WhatsApp to Instagram if you didn't register as a PSE.

But, why does this have to be enlivened? What's the problem? Well, here we summarize the things you need to know. https://t.co/fuxfdleril
